<div style="text-align: center; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
    <img src="https://polygol.github.io/assets/appicon/tips.png" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 50%;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: 600;">Gestures</h1>
    <p style="opacity: 0.8; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Polygol is designed to feel fluid. Navigate the interface using natural movements.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: left; background: var(--search-background); padding: 20px; border-radius: 25px; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded" style="font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px; color: var(--text-color);">swipe_up</span>
            <div>
                <strong style="display: block; font-size: 1rem;">Open App Drawer or Minimize App</strong>
                <span style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">Swipe up from the bottom pill.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded" style="font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px; color: var(--text-color);">swipe_down</span>
            <div>
                <strong style="display: block; font-size: 1rem;">Donburi Dashboard</strong>
                <span style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">Swipe down on the desktop to access the Donburi dashboard.</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded" style="font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px; color: var(--text-color);">touch_long</span>
            <div>
                <strong style="display: block; font-size: 1rem;">Wallpaper Switcher</strong>
                <span style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">Long press anywhere on an empty part of the desktop.</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded" style="font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px; color: var(--text-color);">swipe</span>
            <div>
                <strong style="display: block; font-size: 1rem;">Quick Switch</strong>
                <span style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">Swipe left or right on the desktop to cycle wallpapers.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>